      FlexibleContexts
      FlexibleInstances
      MultiParamTypeClasses
      ConstrainedClassMethods
      InstanceSigs
      TypeSynonymInstances
      DeriveDataTypeable
      DeriveFoldable
      DeriveFunctor
      DeriveTraversable
      StandaloneDeriving
      EmptyDataDeriving
      DeriveLift
      GeneralisedNewtypeDeriving
      DeriveGeneric
      TemplateHaskell
      TypeFamilies
      OverloadedLabels
      OverloadedLists
